Companion Passive Mode
    Events
        Unit - A unit Starts the effect of an ability
    Conditions
        (Ability being cast) Equal to Passive Mode 
    Actions
        Sound - Play GoodJob <gen>
        -------- Turn off other Modes --------
        Trigger - Turn off Companion Aggressive Mode Active <gen>
        Trigger - Turn off Companion Normal Mode Active <gen>
        Trigger - Turn on Companion Passive Mode Active <gen>
        -------- Start current mode --------
        Game - Display to (All players) the text: Companions: Passive...
        Trigger - Run Companion Passive Mode Active <gen> (checking conditions)
